snippet.title: Killing Floor 3 - Closed Beta Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Players eager to test their zed-slaying skills early can sign up for access and information about Killing Floor 3's upcoming closed beta via this link: https://killingfloor3.com/#signup 

The Killing Floor 3 Closed beta takes place Feb. 20-24.
